contentrichtext.text: '''Milu''' may refer to: ==People== *[[Milú]] (Maria de Lourdes de Almeida Lemos) (1926–2008), Portuguese actress and singer *[[miLù]] German singer who has worked with [[Schiller (band)]] ==Other uses== *[[Milü]], an approximation for pi by Zu Chongzhi *[[Milu (mythology)]], the ruler of [[Lua-o-Milu]], the underworld *[[Père David's Deer]], milu ({{zh|c={{linktext|麋|鹿}}|p=mílù}}) or '''elaphure''', ''Elaphurus davidianus'', also known as Père David's deer, a Chinese species of deer known only in captivity *[[Milu, Iran]], a village in Hormozgan Province, Iran ==See also== *[[Snowy (character)]] (''Milou'' in French), fictional character of ''Les Aventures de Tintin'' comic strip series {{Disambig}}
